speech.p: Well, my Lords, if your Lordships feel that, you will vote against the Motion and we will bring it back on the next occasion. But I think I must press it, in the sense that it is a carefully considered set of proposals that I do not accept are fundamental changes and which, on the matters that the noble Lord mentioned, reflect the existing positionâ€”so I beg to move.

lordlist.lord: Lord McCrea of Magherafelt and Cookstown
